# Normalize line endings — store & check out LF everywhere, deterministically.
# Overrides each contributor's local core.autocrlf so the READMEs never
# churn into whole-file CRLF diffs.
* text=auto eol=lf
*.md  text eol=lf
*.svg text eol=lf

# Raster/binary assets (add more as the repo grows)
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
